Table NameINFOTN_COLL.MV_DOCUMENTI_CUSTOM
Functional Name
Abbreviation
Classification Type Name
Object Type Name
MV Prebuilt
MV Query
SELECT dpa_associazione_templates.ROWID AS asstrowid,
       dpa_oggetti_custom.ROWID AS oggcrowid,
       dpa_ogg_custom_comp.ROWID AS oggccrowid,
       dpa_tipo_atto.ROWID AS tarowid,
       dpa_tipo_oggetto.ROWID AS torowid,
       --dpa_associazione_templates.id_oggetto
       dpa_associazione_templates.system_id AS system_id_template, -- AS asstrowid,
       dpa_oggetti_custom.system_id AS system_id_ogg_custom, --    AS oggcrowid,
       dpa_ogg_custom_comp.system_id AS system_id_ogg_custom_comp,

Table NameINFOTN_COLL.MV_PROSPETTI_DOCGRIGI
Functional Name
Abbreviation
Classification Type Name
Object Type Name
MV Prebuilt
MV Query
SELECT   people.id_amm, dpa_l_ruolo_reg.id_registro,
         TRUNC (PROFILE.creation_date, 'MM') creation_month, PROFILE.var_sede,
         getchaimg (docnumber) AS flag_immagine,
         COUNT (DISTINCT PROFILE.system_id) AS distinct_count
         ,      COUNT (PROFILE.system_id) AS undistinct_count
    -- into totMonDocGrigi
FROM     PROFILE, people, dpa_l_ruolo_reg
   WHERE PROFILE.id_ruolo_prot = dpa_l_ruolo_reg.id_ruolo_in_uo
     AND PROFILE.author = people.system_id
     AND PROFILE.num_proto IS NULL
     AND PROFILE.cha_tipo_proto = 'G'
     AND id_documento_principale IS NULL
     AND NVL (PROFILE.cha_in_cestino, '0') <> '1'
GROUP BY people.id_amm,
         dpa_l_ruolo_reg.id_registro,
         TRUNC (PROFILE.creation_date, 'MM'),
         PROFILE.var_sede,
         getchaimg (docnumber)

Table NameINFOTN_COLL.MV_PROSPETTI_DOCGRIGICLASS
Functional Name
Abbreviation
Classification Type Name
Object Type Name
MV Prebuilt
MV Query
SELECT   pe.id_amm
, lrr.id_registro
, pr_t.id_titolario,
         TRUNC (p.creation_date, 'MM') AS grigio_month
         , p.var_sede,
         NVL (p.cha_in_cestino, '0') AS nvl_cha_in_cestino,
         COUNT (DISTINCT p.system_id) AS distinct_count,
         COUNT (p.system_id) AS undistinct_count
    FROM project_components prc,
         PROFILE p,
         project pr_c,                                -- nodi di tipo Cartella
         project pr_f,                                  -- nodi di tipo Folder
         project pr_t,                               -- nodi di tipo titolario
         people pe,
         dpa_l_ruolo_reg lrr
   WHERE prc.LINK = p.system_id
     AND p.id_ruolo_prot = lrr.id_ruolo_in_uo
     AND p.author = pe.system_id
     AND prc.LINK = p.system_id
     AND prc.project_id = pr_c.system_id
     AND pr_c.id_fascicolo = pr_f.system_id
     AND pr_f.id_parent = pr_t.system_id
     AND p.dta_annulla IS NULL
     AND p.num_proto IS NULL
     AND p.cha_tipo_proto = 'G'
     AND id_documento_principale IS NULL
     AND pr_c.cha_tipo_proj = 'C'
     AND pr_f.cha_tipo_proj = 'F'
     AND pr_t.cha_tipo_proj = 'T'
     AND pr_t.cha_tipo_proj = 'T'
     AND pr_t.var_codice IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY pe.id_amm,
         lrr.id_registro,
         pr_t.id_titolario,
         TRUNC (p.dta_proto, 'MM'),
         p.var_sede,
         NVL (p.cha_in_cestino, '0'),
         TRUNC (p.creation_date, 'MM')

Table NameINFOTN_COLL.MV_PROSPETTI_DOCUMENTI
Functional Name
Abbreviation
Classification Type Name
Object Type Name
MV Prebuilt
MV Query
SELECT   NVL (p.id_registro, 0) AS id_registro_0fornull,
         TRUNC (p.creation_date, 'YY') creation_year,
         TRUNC (p.dta_proto, 'MM') proto_month, p.num_anno_proto,
         p.id_uo_prot, p.cha_da_proto,
         NVL (p.cha_in_cestino, '0') cha_in_cestino_0fornull, p.var_sede,
         p.cha_tipo_proto, NVL (getchaimg (p.docnumber), 0) AS flag_immagine,
         CASE
            WHEN dta_annulla IS NULL
               THEN 0
            ELSE 1
         END AS flag_annullato,
         CASE
            WHEN num_proto IS NULL
               THEN 0
            ELSE 1
         END AS flag_num_proto, COUNT (p.system_id) undistinct_count
    FROM PROFILE p
GROUP BY NVL (p.id_registro, 0),
         TRUNC (p.creation_date, 'YY'),
         TRUNC (p.dta_proto, 'MM'),
         p.num_anno_proto,
         p.id_uo_prot,
         p.cha_da_proto,
         NVL (p.cha_in_cestino, '0'),
         p.var_sede,
         p.cha_tipo_proto,
         NVL (getchaimg (p.docnumber), 0),
         CASE
            WHEN dta_annulla IS NULL
               THEN 0
            ELSE 1
         END,
         CASE
            WHEN num_proto IS NULL
               THEN 0
            ELSE 1
         END

Table NameINFOTN_COLL.MV_PROSPETTI_DOCUMENTICLASS
Functional Name
Abbreviation
Classification Type Name
Object Type Name
MV Prebuilt
MV Query
SELECT   pr_t.id_amm, pr_t.id_titolario, pr_t.id_registro,
         TRUNC (p.dta_proto, 'MM') AS proto_month,
         TRUNC (p.creation_date, 'MM') AS creation_month, p.var_sede,
         NVL (p.cha_in_cestino, '0') AS nvl_cha_in_cestino, p.cha_tipo_proto,
         CASE
            WHEN p.dta_annulla IS NULL
               THEN 0
            ELSE 1
         END AS flag_annullato,
         CASE
            WHEN p.num_proto IS NULL
               THEN 0
            ELSE 1
         END AS flag_num_proto,
         CASE
            WHEN p.dta_proto IS NULL
               THEN 0
            ELSE 1
         END AS flag_dta_proto, COUNT (DISTINCT p.system_id)
                                                            AS distinct_count,
         COUNT (p.system_id) AS not_distinct_count
    FROM project_components prc,
         PROFILE p,
         project pr_c,
         project pr_f,
         project pr_t
   WHERE prc.LINK = p.system_id
     AND prc.project_id = pr_c.system_id
     AND pr_c.id_fascicolo = pr_f.system_id
     AND pr_f.id_parent = pr_t.system_id
     AND pr_c.cha_tipo_proj = 'C'
     AND pr_f.cha_tipo_proj = 'F'
     AND pr_t.cha_tipo_proj = 'T'
     AND pr_t.cha_tipo_proj = 'T'
     AND pr_t.var_codice IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY pr_t.id_amm,
         pr_t.id_titolario,
         pr_t.id_registro,
         TRUNC (p.dta_proto, 'MM'),
         TRUNC (p.creation_date, 'MM'),
         p.var_sede,
         NVL (p.cha_in_cestino, '0'),
         p.cha_tipo_proto,
         CASE
            WHEN p.dta_annulla IS NULL
               THEN 0
            ELSE 1
         END,
         CASE
            WHEN p.num_proto IS NULL
               THEN 0
            ELSE 1
         END,
         CASE
            WHEN p.dta_proto IS NULL
               THEN 0
            ELSE 1
         END

Select cg.Id_Amm , P.Id_Registro , Num_Anno_Proto, Count(*) Totprotuo, cg.System_Id, cg.Var_Desc_Corr
From  Profile P Join Dpa_Corr_Globali Cg On Id_Uo_Prot = Cg.System_Id
